    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is for parts or as a major restoration project. It currently suffers from significant mechanical failures, including a slipping transmission and an engine with severe oil leaks and low compression that will require a full rebuild. The exterior shows heavy wear with visible rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, while the interior has torn upholstery and several non-functional electrical components. This car is not currently roadworthy and will need to be towed.",
      "price": 3500.0,
